<div class="library-tome-centered">
From the moment I first laid eyes on Sophia, I knew she was special. I remember going to the owner's house, seeing a few puppies, but it was Sophia who caught my heart instantly. I paid a deposit and waited two long, hard weeks, filled with anticipation, just to bring her home. The pictures I received during that time only fueled my excitement, and when I finally met her, it felt like we were meant to be best friends from the start.<div><br></div><div>Sophia is a lap dog, and our daily routines revolve around cuddling, playing, and occasionally going for walks. Even now, as I write this, she is right here beside me, providing comfort and warmth. We are inseparable, and even when I have to leave her for errands, I hurry back because I don't want to be away from her for too long. She truly is a constant source of joy and companionship.</div><div><br></div><div>Whenever I have difficult days, a short nap with Sophia by my side makes everything better. She licks my face, cuddles into my neck, and we just lay there, thinking about life. These moments of comfort and connection are priceless.</div><div><br></div><div>Sophia has a unique way of showing love, especially with her pre-bedtime face licking, which is a nightly routine that melts my heart. In a world where people can be unreliable and forming lasting friendships is challenging, Sophia has been my unwavering friend. She is always there, ready to cuddle and play, making every day brighter.</div><div><br></div><div>Before Sophia, I was alone and depressed, struggling to find anyone to talk to or spend time with. Bringing her into my life changed everything. She turned my days from lonely and bleak to something truly amazing.</div><div><br></div><div>Some of my favorite memories are when Sophia makes appearances in my videos. It's heartwarming to see how much the audience loves her, and having her by my side during these moments is incredibly special.</div><div><br></div><div>When I'm feeling down or stressed, Sophia's solution is always cuddles. Her unconditional love and affection remind me that I am never alone.</div><div><br></div><div>Sophia, no amount of writing can fully express how much I love you. Instead, I will show you through my actions. Every single day, I will strive to provide you with the best life possible. You are my loyal companion, my source of joy, and my best friend. Thank you for being you.</div>
</div>
